any class can solo in AO, and leveling for any class isn't hard. you can get 1-10 levels a day depending if you're grouped and for how long. most missions, you get equipment that you won't even be able to use til later levels, so you never really have to worry about equipment.<br>
the game is set up so that you don't have to worry about grinding, getting loot, or porting around. it's all about fun, and they did one hell of a job.<br>
